AND CLOSE OF 3 BARS AGO > CLOSE OF 4 BARS AGO
AND CLOSE OF 4 BARS AGO > CLOSE OF 8 BARS AGO

AND STOP LOSS AT ENTRY PRICE - 6.118826 %
